{"title":"歙砚歌","authors":["张虎"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":9,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"歙砚歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张虎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安徽黄山市的屯溪，有一条“老街”，店铺沿袭宋以来的建筑风格；现经营文房四宝、书画杂项，颇具古风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙尾山上石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歙砚名天下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天佑始开采，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年传佳话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五彩尤难寻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"角浪浪淘沙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金星绕玉带，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眉子劭文华。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山高揽小月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纤秀描危崖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叱咤蛟龙起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风凛虎翼花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扣之丁冬韵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抚之儿面颊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈之生云气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"润墨久不乏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小者如核拳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大者如盘瓜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玉质幽光里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莹柔是几匝？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陶公制巨砚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边款好题跋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清溪远游子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得宝诗兴发。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虚谷赏钟秀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪梅令惊讶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山水遥相望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老翁吟白发。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苍松领人意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荆扉入农家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一方砚在手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丹青泥古化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难怪藏砚人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千金不出嫁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿以终身伴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时时赏奇葩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提笔数千行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"染翰好图画。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我藏“庙前红”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罕见不须夸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我唱歙砚歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦笔生彩霞！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}